# API Route Conventions

## Auth

Every API handler gets the user via `requireUser(locals.user)` from `$lib/server/auth-guard`. Never use `locals.user!`.

```typescript
import { requireUser } from '$lib/server/auth-guard'

export const GET: RequestHandler = async ({ locals }) => {
  const userId = requireUser(locals.user).id
  // ...
}
```

## Endpoints

| Route | Methods | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| `/api/chat` | POST | Stream LLM response (SSE) with tool loop |
| `/api/chat/title` | POST | Generate conversation title via LLM |
| `/api/conversations` | GET, POST | List/create conversations |
| `/api/conversations/[id]` | GET, PATCH, DELETE | Single conversation CRUD |
| `/api/messages/[conversationId]` | GET | List messages |
| `/api/api-keys` | GET, POST | List provider/tool key status / upsert key |
| `/api/api-keys/[provider]` | DELETE | Remove key |
| `/api/models/[provider]` | GET | List models for provider |
| `/api/models/manage` | GET, PUT, PATCH | Model allowlist management |
| `/api/settings` | GET, PUT | User settings |
| `/api/system-prompts` | GET, POST | List/create system prompts |
| `/api/system-prompts/[id]` | PATCH, DELETE | Update/delete system prompt |
| `/api/uploads` | POST | Multipart file upload |
| `/api/uploads/[id]` | GET | Serve uploaded file |
| `/api/files/[fileId]` | GET | Download from Anthropic Files API (code execution output) |
| `/api/dictation` | POST | Audio transcription via Mistral Voxtral |

## Streaming

`POST /api/chat` returns `Content-Type: text/event-stream`. Each chunk is `data: <JSON>\n\n` where JSON is a `ChatStreamEvent`. Event types include `text_delta`, `thinking_delta`, `tool_call`, `tool_result`, `code_execution_start`, `code_execution_delta`, `code_execution_result`, `code_execution_files`, `usage`, `done`, `error`, and `raw_assistant_content`.
